		</a>
		<h1 class="title">创始人沈黎晖说，要把摩登天空做成从音乐出发的消费公司</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">霍小斯</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-26 08:45:14 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
		<img src="/system/articles/longshows/11227/medium/11227.jpeg?1435200860" alt="" />
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="11227" data-title="《创始人沈黎晖说，要把摩登天空做成从音乐出发的消费公司》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/11227/medium/11227.jpg?1436641606" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/11227.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
